Class myStringBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • myStringBuilder

  • public class myStringBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by MSD on 8.03.2017. myStringBuilder class which works like the StringBuilder class. class have: A single list, 3 to string method and append methods that exist in StringBuilder.
